name: 2010 Poster Series
description: A series of four posters each representing a quarter of the year, focusing on typography. For more info on the project, and a closer look at each of the pieces, check out my flickr photoset and then head on back and pick up a copy! Each poster is printed on archival-quality Epson Enhanced Matte paper on an Epson 4880 printer, and will be shipped in a poster tube. Also, take a read of my blog post about the process and design.
